Perquisites:

1. Install Visual Studio Code
2. Install Visual Studio Code C# Extension 
3. Install .NET Framework SDK [Time of Writing .NET Framework SDK is 7.0]

To Start a C# Project:
1. Create a Folder [Project Name is Folder Name]
2. Go to Visual Studio Code Terminal and type this in [NOT including "]: "dotnet new console"
3. All Folders and Files should generate, in "program.cs", Start coding in C#